==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Portent
<hw>Por*tent"</hw> <pr>(?; 277)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>portentum</ets>. See <er>Portend</er>.]</ety> <def>That which
portends, or foretoken; esp., that which portends evil; a sign of coming
calamity; an omen; a sign.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>My loss by dire <qex>portents</qex> the god foretold.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Portentive</ent>⟦br⟧
